"url" : "_can_f_canopen_local_device_canopen_diagnosis.html", 
"breadcrumbs" : "CODESYS CANbus \/ CANopen 本地设备（从站） \/ 诊断 \/ CANopen 诊断 ", 
"snippet" : "本章介绍 CANopen 协议提供的诊断选项。...", 
